00:13:07,861 --> 00:13:10,181
If you're a little animal living on the forest floor here

246
00:13:10,281 --> 00:13:12,882
and you can't really make out all of this perspective,

247
00:13:13,222 --> 00:13:15,302
you're not going to understand when the next meal pops up.

248
00:13:15,923 --> 00:13:18,203
