272
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:28,311
because real life is so seemingly chaotic

273
00:14:28,671 --> 00:14:31,132
that navigating all of the uncertainty of the real world

274
00:14:31,192 --> 00:14:32,573
is really emotionally taxing.

275
00:14:33,656 --> 00:14:37,277
Real life is not so complex. That's a problem that we might as well just act randomly.

