00:45:06,079 --> 00:45:08,300
This is pretty much what Piaget was talking about, right?

832
00:45:08,360 --> 00:45:12,342
It's just this idea that the amount of information that I get to learn in combat,

833
00:45:12,422 --> 00:45:15,584
in a game that has this really big possibility space, is so diverse

834
00:45:15,944 --> 00:45:19,266
that we're constantly assimilating or accommodating new information.

835
00:45:19,406 --> 00:45:21,447
We constantly update our mental models.

836
00:45:21,807 --> 00:45:22,748
Things don't get stale.

837
00:45:24,128 --> 00:45:28,374
